metadata.name: Pick My Brain
metadata.description:
Introducing Pick My Brain. Ownership of my 1/1 actual brain scans so you can literally and figuratively pick my brain.

Throughout my career I've been fortunate to have been a part of some incredible projects and teams and I'd love to extend my expertise to you, your project, and your community. 

Need help organizing an event? Ask me. 

Want some brand sponsors? Shoot me a text. 

Want to run some biz dev ideas by me? Let's schedule a call. 

Whatever you need, we can figure it out. 

By picking my brain, together we'll bridge web3 and IRL through actionable guidance and connections. 

Let's make some magic happen.
